  "root_text": {
    "sn21.5:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 21.5 ",
    "sn21.5:0.2": "1. Bhikkhuvagga ",
    "sn21.5:0.3": "Sujātasutta ",
    "sn21.5:1.1": "Sāvatthiyaṁ viharati. ",
    "sn21.5:1.2": "Atha kho āyasmā sujāto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami. ",
    "sn21.5:1.3": "Addasā kho bhagavā āyasmantaṁ sujātaṁ dūratova āgacchantaṁ. ",
    "sn21.5:1.4": "Disvāna bhikkhū āmantesi: ",
    "sn21.5:1.5": "“ubhayenevāyaṁ, bhikkhave, kulaputto sobhati—",
    "sn21.5:1.6": "yañca abhirūpo dassanīyo pāsādiko paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgato, yassa catthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṁ pabbajanti tadanuttaraṁ brahmacariyapariyosānaṁ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṁ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharatī”ti. ",
    "sn21.5:1.7": "Idamavoca bhagavā …pe… ",
    "sn21.5:1.8": "satthā: ",
    "sn21.5:2.1": "“Sobhati vatāyaṁ bhikkhu, ",
    "sn21.5:2.2": "ujubhūtena cetasā; ",
    "sn21.5:2.3": "Vippayutto visaṁyutto, ",
    "sn21.5:2.4": "anupādāya nibbuto; ",
    "sn21.5:2.5": "Dhāreti antimaṁ dehaṁ, ",
    "sn21.5:2.6": "jetvā māraṁ savāhinin”ti. ",
    "sn21.5:2.7": "Pañcamaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "sn21.5:0.1": "Linked Discourses 21.5 ",
    "sn21.5:0.2": "1. Monks ",
    "sn21.5:0.3": "With Sujāta ",
    "sn21.5:1.1": "At Sāvatthī. ",
    "sn21.5:1.2": "Then Venerable Sujāta went to see the Buddha. ",
    "sn21.5:1.3": "The Buddha saw him coming off in the distance, ",
    "sn21.5:1.4": "and addressed the mendicants: ",
    "sn21.5:1.5": "“This gentleman shines in both ways. ",
    "sn21.5:1.6": "He’s attractive, good-looking, lovely, of surpassing beauty. And he has realized the supreme end of the spiritual path in this very life. He lives having achieved with his own insight the goal for which gentlemen rightly go forth from the lay life to homelessness.” ",
    "sn21.5:1.7": "That is what the Buddha said. ",
    "sn21.5:1.8": "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: ",
    "sn21.5:2.1": "“This mendicant truly shines. ",
    "sn21.5:2.2": "His heart is upright, ",
    "sn21.5:2.3": "he’s unfettered, detached, ",
    "sn21.5:2.4": "quenched by not grasping. ",
    "sn21.5:2.5": "He bears his final body, ",
    "sn21.5:2.6": "having vanquished Māra with his legions.” "
  },
